1
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:39,664
=Visage and Soul=

2
00:00:39,665 --> 00:00:43,040
(The "Different Her"
Trilogy on Women's Relationships)

3
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:47,640
=Episode 5=

4
00:00:53,080 --> 00:00:54,200
All I ever wanted

5
00:00:55,920 --> 00:00:58,120
was for you to remember me.

6
00:01:21,520 --> 00:01:22,800
Feeling sorry for me already?

7
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:24,920
At least you've got a conscience.

8
00:01:25,600 --> 00:01:27,720
I'm just worried you'll
die at my company.

9
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:34,880
Quit pretending.

10
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,720
I know you care about me.

11
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,240
So, are you dying or not?

12
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:44,040
Die.

13
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:46,400
Just kiss me,

14
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:48,440
and I'll drop dead right now.

15
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,640
Since you know so much about art,

16
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:04,720
why not stay and help me?

17
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:09,360
Miss Qiao,

18
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:10,880
are you serious?

19
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:12,680
I don't come cheap.

20
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,720
How about I buy you dinner?

21
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:22,960
Let's go.

22
00:02:47,320 --> 00:02:48,920
Why do you keep staring at me?

23
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,720
Just thinking.

24
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:52,480
You're a rich heiress,

25
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,080
and this

26
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,440
is your idea of a big meal?

27
00:02:59,760 --> 00:03:01,160
Then what do you want to eat?

28
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,280
I want...

29
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,760
Tell me.

30
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:12,200
Are you working with Qiao Zhiwei?

31
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:16,960
I'm on your side.

32
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:24,480
Then where have you been

33
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,280
for the past three years?

34
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:30,960
What else would I be doing?

35
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:32,920
Missing you.

36
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:42,880
Why did you get close to me?

37
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:46,160
What are you really after?

38
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,560
I have three objectives.

39
00:03:49,880 --> 00:03:50,640
You.

40
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:52,080
You.

41
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:57,080
And you.

42
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:04,880
Was what I said really that gross?

43
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,360
You think I'm disgusting?

44
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:14,800
You actually look kinda
cute when you throw up.

45
00:04:24,520 --> 00:04:25,320
Hold it in.

46
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:27,600
I'm warning you.

47
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,280
If you throw up on me,

48
00:04:29,280 --> 00:04:30,880
I'll dump you on the side of the road.

49
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:36,840
Were you always this mean to me?

50
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:41,200
Of course.

51
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,400
Back then,

52
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:45,000
if you didn't listen,

53
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:47,240
I'd beat the crap out of you.

54
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:53,160
No wonder my dad didn't
want us together.

55
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:57,800
Because I'm his favorite daughter.

56
00:04:57,800 --> 00:05:00,120
He'd never let anyone...

57
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:37,240
You brought me to a hotel?

58
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,960
This is my place.

59
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:40,440
I couldn't find an apartment,

60
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,640
so I'm staying here for now.

61
00:05:42,400 --> 00:05:44,160
Just you wait.

62
00:05:44,520 --> 00:05:47,120
I'm going to fight you till...

63
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:48,560
till...

64
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:49,840
daybreak.

65
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,280
Get some sleep.

66
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:54,520
We'll settle this tomorrow.

67
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:05,640
Come on, fight me.

68
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:06,880
Don't you want to?

69
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:17,880
I...

70
00:06:18,960 --> 00:06:20,560
What are you hiding from?

71
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:22,360
Well.

72
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:25,640
Aren't you my fiancé?

73
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:30,640
What haven't I seen?

74
00:06:34,640 --> 00:06:36,040
The hell you have.

75
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:36,960
Stay right there.

76
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:38,680
Don't move.

77
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:40,640
What?

78
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:42,880
Don't tell me we've never...

79
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:55,360
Nice body.

80
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:55,840
You...

81
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:57,160
Don't start acting crazy
just because you're drunk.

82
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,560
I'm warning you.

83
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:07,480
What do you want?

84
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:08,960
What do I want?

85
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:10,640
You really don't know?

86
00:08:13,640 --> 00:08:15,040
Why are you pretending?

87
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:19,640
So who's pretending here, you or me?

88
00:08:20,640 --> 00:08:21,560
Weren't you drunk?

89
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:27,800
Pop quiz.

90
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:31,040
What's my favorite flower?

91
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:31,800
Roses.

92
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:32,440
What's my favorite color?

93
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:32,920
Black.

94
00:08:32,920 --> 00:08:33,840
Do I prefer cats or dogs?

95
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,480
Both.

96
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,400
Hot pot or barbecue?

97
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:36,880
Hot pot in summer, barbecue in winter.

98
00:08:38,680 --> 00:08:39,800
Not one answer was right.

99
00:08:41,920 --> 00:08:43,360
I don't like roses
because they have thorns.

100
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:45,240
I don't like black
because it's too depressing.

101
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,080
I've never had a cat or a dog,

102
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,320
so I wouldn't know.

103
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:50,280
As for hot pot and barbecue,

104
00:08:50,280 --> 00:08:51,240
I don't like either.

105
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:53,200
Because I don't like

106
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:54,880
fire.

107
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,960
You're lying.

108
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,240
Aren't you?

109
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,640
No, you're the one

110
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:05,320
who's lying.

111
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,360
Because I like roses.

112
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,280
I like black.

113
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:09,280
I like cats and dogs.

114
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:10,800
I like hot pot in the summer

115
00:09:10,800 --> 00:09:12,520
and barbecue in the winter.

116
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:14,840
You told me all that back then.

117
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,520
Because I liked them,

118
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,320
you liked them too.

119
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,400
So...

120
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:24,800
are you lying now,

121
00:09:26,640 --> 00:09:28,600
or was it your past self who lied?

122
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:36,160
Why argue with someone who has amnesia?

123
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,360
Game over.

124
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:41,760
No matter who you are,

125
00:09:42,280 --> 00:09:43,520
let's never see each other again.

126
00:10:21,800 --> 00:10:23,870
♪We say good morning,
we say good night♪

127
00:10:23,870 --> 00:10:27,290
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

128
00:10:28,890 --> 00:10:30,780
♪The sweeter it is,
the luckier we seem♪

129
00:10:30,780 --> 00:10:34,770
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

130
00:10:36,010 --> 00:10:37,870
♪Let me go, set me free♪

131
00:10:37,870 --> 00:10:41,910
♪Let me drown in reckless silence♪

132
00:10:42,450 --> 00:10:47,860
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

133
00:10:49,210 --> 00:10:51,350
♪The freedom you gave me♪

134
00:10:51,350 --> 00:10:54,990
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

135
00:10:56,250 --> 00:10:58,520
♪Love can barely move forward♪

136
00:10:58,520 --> 00:11:02,300
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

137
00:11:03,400 --> 00:11:05,640
♪The closeness I long for♪

138
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:10,030
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

139
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:12,260
♪I don't want to break free♪

140
00:11:12,260 --> 00:11:17,630
♪Take back the chains
disguised as freedom♪

